sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant C1 as Client 1
  participant C2 as Client 2
  participant Cache
  participant Lock as Per-key Mutex
  participant Src as Source

  C1->>Cache: get(k)
  Cache-->>C1: miss
  C1->>Lock: acquire(k)
  C2->>Cache: get(k)
  Cache-->>C2: miss
  C2->>Lock: wait(k)
  C1->>Src: load(k)
  Src-->>C1: value
  C1->>Cache: put(k, value)
  C1->>Lock: release(k)
  Lock-->>C2: acquired
  C2->>Cache: get(k)
  Cache-->>C2: hit(value)